Description: R interface to Python modules, classes, and functions. When calling into
  Python R data types are automatically converted to their equivalent Python types. 
  When values are returned from Python to R they are converted back to R types. The
  rpy package is compatible with all versions of Python >= 2.7 and in addition 
  requires NumPy >= 1.11.
License: Apache License 2.0
URL: https://github.com/rstudio/rpy
BugReports: https://github.com/rstudio/rpy/issues
SystemRequirements: Python (>= 2.7.0); NumPy (>= 1.11) (http://www.numpy.org/)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
